  "description": "Heat orchestration health by stack status: how many stacks are complete, failed or in a transitional state, a table of the failed stacks to act on, and the status mix over time. Answers \"did orchestration break, and which stacks are stuck or failed?\" so failed deployments do not sit unnoticed.",
